## Running Tests

```bash
# Run all tests
pnpm test:e2e

# Run specific test file
pnpm test:e2e jar-creation.spec.ts

# Debug mode
pnpm test:e2e:debug

# UI mode (visual test runner)
pnpm test:e2e:ui

# Generate HTML report
pnpm test:e2e:report

# Run only accessibility tests
pnpm test:accessibility
```

